mickey 's twice upon a christmas is a direct-to-video direct-to-video animated film produced by walt disney home entertainment and released by walt disney home entertainment on november 9 , 2004 . it is a sequel to the 1999 film mickey 's millions upon a christmas . mickey 's twice upon a christmas was released on november 9 , 2004 by walt disney home entertainment on november 9 , 2004 .